#Stateless funcitonal component
    -It is just pure function. It just recives an props an returns an node.
    -It is called stateless function because it doesnot perform oprations like pushing value to array
        if any other things are done it may create error or bug.
    -if the props passed is changed the this stateless function is automatically invoked.


#component lifecycle

    #Mount
        -contructor function
        -render
        -componentDidMount

    #Update
        -ComponentWillReceiveProps(nextProps)
        -ShouldComponentUpdate( nextProps , nextState)
        -render
        -componentDidUpdate( prevState , prevProps )
    #Unmount
        -componentWillUnmount()

        
